# 📊 Sales Data Analysis using Python, SQL & Power BI

## 📌 Project Overview

This project focuses on analyzing the **ApexPlanet_DataAnalytics_Dataset-1** to gain meaningful 
business insights using **Python, SQL, and Power BI**. The dataset was cleaned, explored,
and visualized to understand sales performance, customer behavior, and product trends. 
Statistical hypothesis testing was also performed to validate the analysis and support data-driven decision-making.

---

## 🎯 Business Problem

Retail businesses generate large volumes of sales data every day. Without proper analysis, 
it is difficult to identify sales trends, customer purchasing patterns, top-performing products, 
and regional performance. The objective of this project is to analyze sales data, uncover meaningful insights,
and provide actionable recommendations that can improve business performance and support informed decision-making.

---

## 🎯 Project Objectives

- 📈 Analyze overall sales performance.
- 🛍️ Identify top-selling products and product categories.
- 🌍 Compare sales performance across different cities.
- 👥 Understand customer purchasing behavior.
- 🧹 Perform data cleaning and exploratory data analysis.
- 🗄️ Execute SQL queries to generate business insights.
- 📊 Build an interactive Power BI dashboard.
- 📉 Validate findings using statistical hypothesis testing.
- 💡 Provide practical business recommendations.

---

